-960212796.text: "It is thus possible that IL-1beta and AHR work together to tightly repress IL-1R1 hi ILC3 differentiation to stage 4 mature NK cells - that is to say, IL-1beta induces AHR and thus helps expand IL-22-producing IL-1R1 hi ILC3s in response to appropriate environmental stimuli when these cells are necessary for mucosal immunity."
